body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Robert Jenkins and I'm calling from XYZ Insurance Company. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, my name is Samantha Torres.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Samantha. Could you please provide me with your date of birth for security verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's zero five slash one one slash one nine eight zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Samantha. One more piece of information we need is your home address. Could you please share that with me?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Certainly, my address is one two three Main Street, Cityville.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Samantha. We'll use it to update your account details. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, thank you. I appreciate your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Samantha. Thank you for your time today. Have a great day!

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for your time today. Have a great day!
